Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子體內的魔獸現在還在湧動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  魔王還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的話就回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄圖支配神的狂徒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是  這裡的學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓自己的學生受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經沒有力量能防禦我的攻擊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brave  Brave
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是我開發的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就是在村裡留下戰鬥服的那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是初次見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大和望一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是三輪家的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你特意開發了對付魔王的戰鬥服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你一個人不能戰勝魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  你和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都認為魔王還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？  你的意思是說你想幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…說不定還是交給年輕人自己去判斷比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我能感覺到小阿的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是要破壞這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位請看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:06:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保持沉默的照屋家部隊開始進軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎準備衝進校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到反擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是被鎮壓的魔獸的反擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有學生會的允許  禁止進入校內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白石莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我知道
