Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人震驚的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照公佈的說法
